 1990-06501990-03-300,  OLD INAC,  ,  , 
PrecisAcceptance of a Document of Absolute Surrender assented to by the SARNIA BAND OF INDIANS at a referendum held on January 25, 1990, whereby all rights, title and interest of whatsoever kind that the band may have in certain lands which were formerly part of Sarnia Indian Reserve No. 45, in the City of Sarnia, Ontario, will be surrendered to the Crown.
